Experiment 11: WebView in Android Studio
Aim
To develop an Android application using Android Studio that displays web content inside the app using a WebView component.

Algorithm
1.Start
2.Open Android Studio
3.Create a new Android project
4.Design the layout by adding a WebView component in the XML file
5.Assign an ID to the WebView (e.g., webView1)
6.Open the Java/Kotlin file (MainActivity)
7.Import the required WebView packages
8.Initialize the WebView using its ID
